OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsorry to deaf and blind    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fviewers for faults         
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The company at the centre of a string  
OL,6, of faults with TV broadcasts over the  
OL,7, past week has said sorry to deaf and   
OL,8, blind viewers as issues continue to    
OL,9, affect subtitles and audio description.
OL,11,FRed Bee Media said it understands "the 
OL,12,Fchallenges" viewers are facing.        
OL,14,F"We share your frustration and are     
OL,15,Fworking tirelessly towards a solution,"
OL,16,Fit said in a statement on Twitter.     
OL,18,FThe company handles playout services   
OL,19,Fand broadcasting technology for a      
OL,20,Fnumber of channels.                    
